Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:18.36,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:29.82,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:36.75,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:47.88,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.81,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:08.70,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:20.59,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:26.43,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:36.23,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:29.82,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:36.75,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:47.88,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.81,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:08.70,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:20.59,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:26.43,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:36.23,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.49,0:01:51.75,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(100,160)}Ep. 20 - Water in the Well
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are you off to, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.59,0:02:03.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Koala!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:04.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:08.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's for Koalas! We're going to catch a koala!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:12.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Sounds mighty interesting.\NBring me along, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.71,0:02:15.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking of taking a stroll or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:17.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, you climb trees?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:22.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well when I was a kiddo I didn't do anything much\Nother than climbing them trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:24.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Erm... But now, I'm ever so slightly incapable of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:27.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's no point in you coming with us anyway!
Comment: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:30.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:31.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Incapable, you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:35.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Climbing trees, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:37.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Comment: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:39.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why, it seems, I still can, if I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:44.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:46.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:51.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, did you drink yourself blind again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? You think I could pull off\Nsomething like that if I were drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:57.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you do something like that\Nif you're not drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:59.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I can swear I'm not drunk now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:00.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:02.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch, ouch, ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:04.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:07.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm fine. All fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:10.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be climbing there\Nafter you drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:14.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've not drank a drop of it!\NIt's 'cos Lucy-May shook me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:15.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Shook you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:18.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She said I can't tag along with them\Nif I can't climb trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:21.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My! Don't tell me those two\Nleft to look for animals again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:24.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was to catch koala, I reckon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:29.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I was hoping they'd look after Tob for me\Nwhile I'm doing the laundry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:31.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well I could look after him, if you'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:32.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But aren't you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:34.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, relax, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:36.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, ain't got crowds of patients now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:38.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If so, I'd like you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:39.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:43.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tob, wanna play with this old bum today? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:44.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Battly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:48.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Battly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:52.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aight, I'm watching after him, so do your laundry\Nor whatever it is you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:53.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:58.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll manage to catch that,\Nyou're probably a prodigy, Tob!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:00.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Battly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:01.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:02.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:03.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Almost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's Mr. Parker's oxcart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:18.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:23.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, young ladies of the Popple household!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:28.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're in a hurry to get somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to catch a koala.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:31.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Well, I rightly envy you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why so, Mr. Parker?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:37.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike us, grown-ups, you kids can afford\Njust playing around all day, all carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:42.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that! Until just a little while ago,\Nwe also had to help making candles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:44.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:47.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're also having to work quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:51.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's anything but easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:52.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:56.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Back in England, kids just need to go to school\Nand study to be left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:59.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But in Australia, even kids aren't spared\Nthe hardships of life, ain't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:01.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can put it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:04.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's be on our way, Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:04.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:08.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:11.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And be sure to return home before dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:13.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:15.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Move it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:20.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This time, we couldn't help\Nfeeding Mr. Parker a bit of a line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:24.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We don't really have to work all that much.\NWe don't experience any hardships either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:29.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, say what you want,\Nthere ain't no schools here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:31.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what we like the most about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:00.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it here where we last saw a koala?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:03.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sitting here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:08.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If so, I should be able to catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:13.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We get it, alright? You're good at climbing trees now,\Nis that what you're getting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not a single one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:30.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And we can't go any deeper into the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:32.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try looking there, sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:32.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:36.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't turn back here,\Nwe'll lose our way for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:40.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, just a little more!\NWe've made it this far already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I might just know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:43.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How not to lose our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:47.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:51.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If we keep an eye on the position of the sun,\Nwe'll always know which way is which.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:54.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And so, we could easily\Nbacktrack to where we came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.57,0:06:55.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,About right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:57.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do that, sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:07:01.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. If I stand like this now,\Nthe sun is to the right from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:01.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:05.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Which means if we keep walking\Nwith sun always to our right,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:10.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,we'll need but to walk with sun on our left\Nto return exactly the way we came.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:12.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:15.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's go a bit further into the woods, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:43.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There! Can't you see it in the shadow of those leaves?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where? I don't see anything at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with your eyes today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:49.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:54.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,From the bottom: one, two, three, four, five, six, seven -\Nit's where the eighth branch splits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:57.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eighth branch... That high?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:59.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:03.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why, that's just an owl!\NIt's an owl, no two ways about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:09.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You're right. It's just an owl sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:13.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we're out of luck today.\NLet's try looking for it some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:16.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so, too.\NMaybe we'd better resign for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:17.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's return, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:19.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:21.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sun hid among the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:24.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:28.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do now, Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:31.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Retracing the path we walked just now\Nshouldn't be that hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:33.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:35.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back, if so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We passed through here before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We must've passed through here as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:57.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kate! We passed through here, did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:58.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:24.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:28.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's wait here until Mr. Sun decides to show himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:31.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We lost the road, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:35.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there was never\Nany road in the forest to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:39.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you speaking this way now, sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:43.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well maybe it's 'cause I've not a single clue now -
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:45.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,which way should we walk to get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:51.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't seem to me like we've walked that awfully far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:54.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why we were supposed\Nto be out of the woods long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:55.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:58.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try walking this way, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:10:00.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why should we walk that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:04.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that going this way\Nwould be better for us, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:06.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can say just about the same about this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:10.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, do you suggest we stay here for some while?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:13.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Only until Mr. Sun comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:17.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But will it ever come out?\NThe clouds just keep on filling the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:21.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But say, those clouds look a bit like a herd of sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:29.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the actual sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:32.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You're right, it's the sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:36.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But if there are sheep here,\Nthat should mean the grassland is also near!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:40.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So the grassland was this way, after all?\NTurns out, we were both wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:52.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They look mighty nervous, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:55.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The sheep aren't supposed\Nto be nervous from seeing humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:57.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it's beyond doubt they're nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:11:00.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Must be that those sheep\Nstrayed away and got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:02.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:07.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, kids, what's wrong?\NI don't think we're anywhere near that scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:10.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:10.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:11.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:12.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You know, when we just came.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:16.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When we arrived to Adelaide for the first time,\Nwe were chased by some beast, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:17.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:19.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not a wolf, but something similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look, there it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:25.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now, it's a dingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:27.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Must be that it's after these sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:35.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta save the sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:36.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.97,0:11:38.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:41.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It could as well attack us instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:44.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there a stick somewhere?\NEven a stone would do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:51.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,See one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:54.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:56.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Take that! You beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:58.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:16.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,See this? Come closer and I'll smack you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:19.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:25.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:26.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,For how long will we do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:39.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Until it leaves the sheep alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:44.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like we'll wear ourselves out\Nbefore it ever gives up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's hold an endurance contest!
Comment: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:49.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:51.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:58.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the shepherd dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:02.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, the dogs are coming!\NBetter run now, unless you wanna get bitten!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:14.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like they're driving the lost sheep\Ntowards the rest of the herd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:18.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. We should also be fine now,\Nif we follow after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:20.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Which means we're saved, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:34.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good, good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:38.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He's one particularly intelligent fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:42.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Monocle.\NIt was really only thanks to you that we were saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:47.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Consider yourself lucky, Monocle.\NYou're getting patted on the head by a lady so adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I should say my thanks, too.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:59.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you go other there again and keep an eye out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:01.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In case any more sheep lose their way,\NI'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:08.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's a truly marvelous dog you got!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:09.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:12.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Ah! I never thanked you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:14.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well I've not done anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it's the second time we meet you thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:21.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, the other time you were also\Nchased by a dingo, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:24.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Except that you had one more\Nbeautiful young lady with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sister Clara!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:26.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:30.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but what would be your name, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddya wanna know that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:36.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we've been saved by you twice already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:38.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And in both cases I've not been doing much saving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just let us know your name, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:44.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... My name is Larry Long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:46.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been here for long?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:52.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You may call it long, though it's only been two years\Nsince we, the white people, came to live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:53.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:57.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I should say, the city construction pace\Nlags behind thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:15:00.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The land surveying is slugging\Nand we've neither a church nor a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:01.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The school can wait, I reckon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:02.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:05.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It's best that they leave the school till last, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:10.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't seem like you two\Nare very fond of school, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:12.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is it any different for you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:17.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,During my childhood years, the poor\Ncouldn't go to school even if they wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:19.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That includes you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I never went to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:25.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thus I don't know how to write or read.\NWould be awful pity if you end up like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:27.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can write and read already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:28.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I also can read a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:33.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, this city has its own newspaper already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:35.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping you two\Nwould it read it for me sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:37.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll read it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:39.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And what about the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:40.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll read the letters that I can read.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:42.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Only the letters you can read?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:52.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May, you're looking mighty gloomy to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:57.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't find it today,\Nbut we'll be sure to find this koala soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:58.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:16:02.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In case mom allows us,\Nwe can go look for it tomorrow as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:04.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:05.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:08.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think they can do it?\NDo you think they can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:09.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:12.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's about school.\NDo you think they can really build it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:17.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:22.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If it gets built, dad and mom would totally\Nmake me go there, won't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:23.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:25.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd have to go there every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:26.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:27.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'd also have to study, won't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's school, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:43.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Both the spinach and carrots are sprouting\Nthat ridiculously soon... What could that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:48.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not only this place has the seasons exactly opposite\Nto those in Yorkshire where we used to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,but it's also different in many other aspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:56.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Until we know exactly what those differences are,\Nwe're always running a risk of ruining our field.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:17:00.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There, look at these radishes.\NThey're this big already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:04.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They smell great, too!\NWe'll be feeding on great salads soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:07.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I just wish they'd give me the land sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:11.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In a country so wide and spacious,\Nit won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:13.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll be offered\Na magnificent piece of land.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:18.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It was a sound move from the government\Nnot to sell the land until it's neatly surveyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:23.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... Still, it doesn't seem like\Nthe surveying is getting anywhere at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Haste makes waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:29.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just start by rebuilding our lives in this\Nnew country bit by bit, to the best of our abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:32.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Bit by bit for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:36.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.19,0:17:40.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jamling is calling! Come quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:42.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did he hit the water, Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:44.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think so! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:53.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Popple!\NI'd say we did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:56.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of this water, Mr. Jamling?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:18:00.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's good water.\NThis area seems rich in groundwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:02.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Then, how about you climb up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:08.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? Clara, hold on tight to Tob's hand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:09.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want him falling into the well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:12.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. The water finally started to accumulate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Jamling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:21.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Though I've only drank a bit,\NI noticed the water was cold and tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:24.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right. It's good that we chose this spot, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a lot of water accumulated already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:30.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better wait a bit\Nuntil you start drawing the water from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The water is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:33.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to taste it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:36.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The water is still a little muddy,\Nso you can't drink it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:38.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But in just two or three more days, it'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:41.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:47.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's all the commotion, gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:49.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Parker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:52.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The water started to accumulate in our well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:54.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's a great relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:58.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Because well, there's a place where they can't hit water\Nno matter how much they dig.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:19:00.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That must be mighty annoying.\NWhere is that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:02.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's at Mr. Pettywell's plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.61,0:19:05.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They're digging yet another new hole as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:12.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:13.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:13.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.89,0:19:22.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I guess, with this, the Popples family can finally consider all the basic life necessities secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:25.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lot more complicated than that, Mr. Parker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:28.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, this should help\Nmaking the life here a bit more bearable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:32.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Going to the river to fetch water\Nwas becoming quite a feat of heavy labor for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:35.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This also makes short work of watering the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:38.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's also extremely handy for doing the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:42.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We truly are glad Mr. Jamling\Ndecided to help us out of this plight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:46.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was just doing my job for my hirer,\Nwhich is you, Mr. Popple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:50.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what do you plan to do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:53.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I was planning to build one more cabin on this very plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:56.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can handle it on my own, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:59.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, naturally, I'm also counting on Ben to assist me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:00.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A cabin, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:05.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have Dr. Deighton\Nsleep in that tent forever, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:09.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:12.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, now I'm convinced I'm smelling whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:16.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To the completion of well\Nand to the well-being of the Popples family,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:17.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:18.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.39,0:20:19.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:21.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it with those cheers for a bit, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:21.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:23.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Doctor Deighton!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Would you look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:29.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving me out when drinking\Nto the well-being of the Popples is preposterous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:34.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, may I have a glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:42.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, hang on there, will you?\NWe're almost home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:58.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You go enter the house first, Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:20:59.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:03.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's one too may "why's" for your size!\NJust be silent and enter first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:06.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we'll get scolded now,\Nit's not that late yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:08.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's all the more reasons you should go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:11.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's unusual, a wagon is coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:16.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mr. Bernard now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:21.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like he brought someone along.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:22.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:25.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If we come any later,\Nwe're definitely getting scolded!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:29.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright. Mom's getting mad\Nall the same if we return now or a little later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:33.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:34.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bernard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.28,0:21:37.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bernard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:41.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Kate, Lucy-May, that's a perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:45.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I need one of you to inform Dr. Deighton,\Nand the other - to call sister here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:46.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:48.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy, he means Mrs. Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:50.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, this man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:53.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, we've made it home. Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:59.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get Dr. Deighton!\NYou find Mrs. Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.39,0:22:00.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:05.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am! Mrs. Mac, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.90,0:22:09.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Deighton!\NDoctor Deighton?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:15.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well!\NOne of the Popple beauties returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:17.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Deighton!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:19.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.59,0:22:23.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, keep yourself together, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.24,0:22:25.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.88,0:22:29.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you want it, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:33.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, I don't mind. Drench me to your heart's content,\Nstarting from the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:34.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme get a little...
Comment: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:34.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.80,0:22:37.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, keep yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.57,0:22:40.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Now then, now then, what are we waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.27,0:22:41.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.49,0:22:42.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, douse!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:43.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I'm doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:44.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go ahead already!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.62,0:22:49.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whee! Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.92,0:22:51.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:54.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... Yeah, a lot better now. Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.78,0:22:56.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... Do one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:22:58.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.42,0:23:00.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's mighty refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.54,0:23:03.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,One more bucket of cold water\Nwould wear alcohol out completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:09.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.10,0:23:13.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.50,0:23:17.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say it plainly - what's the matter, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.40,0:23:18.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He passed away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:19.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.70,0:23:21.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mac passed away just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.89,0:23:22.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.08,0:23:24.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.18,0:23:34.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go see what's what anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.00,0:23:46.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Although temporary he regained his strength,\Nour neighbor Mr. Mac
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.59,0:23:52.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,fell ill the second time during a surveying expedition\Nto the hinterlands and never made it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.49,0:23:56.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He was only thirty seven years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.70,0:24:05.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When we went fishing with brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.89,0:24:07.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,we accidentally spotted a rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.71,0:24:10.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My sister and I will definitely try to catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.88,0:24:14.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Lucy-May of the Southern Rainbow:\N"The Man Who Designed Adelaide".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.89,0:24:16.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
